{
  "stem": "11771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They lead us-- I don't mean-- no lead us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No lead us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was sheep without a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a shepherd.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The rabbi was sitting-- I didn't even see the rabbi on the-- on the market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw him in the synagogue because he was in the old synagogue-- in the new synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we're sitting all around, waiting for the next day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was already Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How they used to came out, taking groups of 100 at a time, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] setting up five in a line.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever were closer to the gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Panic-- everybody was running away to the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they catch whoever they can when they stood up, with dogs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the panic was-- well, everybody was trying to escape the group to be the next one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To live another half an hour, to live another hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a distance-- I mean, timewise-- three quarters of an hour from one group to the other, an hour, something like this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we heard the shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard the shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was only-- not even about half a mile, the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the peasants, the Polacks, who surrounded the other side the gates of the fence, yelling, screaming, warning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The good one was warning, run, don't go like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Run-- they're shooting you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other was-- throw me out, whatever you-- over the fence, because they're shooting you anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're going to-- you get to be killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of getting it Lithuanian, give it to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were our neighbors, when we used to live with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the good ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were discussing and talking.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
